name: SPIKE ROLLAH
description:
Monstah Rollah 0.8
This is the Evolution of Monstah Rollah, the latest release with many thorns all over his body, looks very cool and different from other Rollah monsters who are braver and stronger! seen from the soulplate with bright red orange color and sky blue mohawk hair showing his form that is ready to fight with other Rollah monsters, this Spike rollah character can add to your collection, All Rollahs will evolve every week
